high_descs: Turn around and head to the coffeetable.
Pick up the mango from the round table.
Turn your left and walk to the sink.
Place the mango on the kitchen sink.
Turn back and head to the coffeetable again.
Pick up the mango from the round table.
Turn around and head to the sink again.
Place the mango on the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the two mangoes on the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left, then go to the bedroom to your right, then walk to the coffeetable to your left.
Pick up the leftmost yellow mango, the one next to the hand purse.
Turn around and go to the doorway to your right and hang a left, then head towards the fridge and go to the sink to your right.
Put the yellow mango on the sink countertop next to the potato.
Turn around and hang a left, then go to the bedroom to your right, then walk to the coffeetable to your left.
Pick up the remaining yellow mango from the round table.
Turn around and go to the doorway to your right and hang a left, then head towards the fridge and go to the sink to your right.
Put the yellow mango on the sink countertop next to the other yellow fruit.
anns.task_desc: Put two yellow Mangoes on the Sink countertop

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable in the bedroom.
Take the mango from the table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the mango on the sink tray.
Turn around and go to the coffeetable.
Take another mango from the table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the mango on the sink tray.
anns.task_desc: Collect the mango and placed it on the sink tray.
